node.text:
If you've ever heard the saying "Teach what you most need to learn" 👉 that's the foundation of the Chopra Coaching Program. You learn to integrate the roles of both teacher, in which you impart information on students, and the coach who evokes wisdom from the client. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
You’ll learn the core conversational skills of listening, asking questions and offering reflections that help clients see themselves more clearly. You’ll gain training in these specific skills and coaching methodology, including what we call the four cornerstones: ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
1. Intention⁠⁠
2. Purpose⁠⁠
3. Meaning⁠⁠
4. Shadow⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Want to learn more about how to become a Well-being Coach? Join our free webinar via link in bio.
